      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The inverter module converts DC (input) to AC (output). The
module is fan cooled.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The input DC voltage settings depends
on the DC input source. The output AC voltage depends on the system
configuration.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Different modules are available for the different
DC inputs and AC outputs combinations.</p>
